    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK482">
<l>paruvattō ṭoṭṭa voḻuka ṟiruviṉait</l>
<l>tīrāmai yārkkuṅ kayiṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Acting at the right season, is a cord that will immoveably bind success (to a king).</l>
